{"tid":824030,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一個十號波 睇得出嚟緊香港社會趨勢","createTime":"2018-09-17T02:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T10:42:51.000Z","uid":37238,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3735cbd32c6f40a62475f03f0b2c423c2385cfed","tid":824030,"uid":37238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:42:22.000Z","msg":"後真相時代<br />\n「屌 個風廢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n「落少少雨就吹到屎上最強 收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n「挑 咪又係雷聲大雨點小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n「我落樓下打羽毛球都仲得呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打乜撚嘢風姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n無論係打風前，打緊定係依架打完，點都會喺連登見到呢啲Po 同留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都知上連登勿認真，我都知上面有啲都係假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係當天文台用科學儀器測哂佢最高陣風/平均風速<br />\n飛虎隊派直升機飛入風眼更新颱風最新數據<br />\n甚至上Google打開衛星雲圖 見到大大舊環流<br />\n越嚟越多人都會寧願唔理呢啲實實在在，客觀嘅data facts<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係用自己所「睇」到「感覺」到嘅主觀感受做批判 定奪是非<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個社會呢幾年一直都向住後真相嘅方向行 只係山竹令到呢樣嘢好明顯咁浮現出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c87f9c5672aeb23d5318e399e7f877b2c95ab54","tid":824030,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6769404a46099a01c9310ac2eecf1ca08e5d43","tid":824030,"uid":442,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"社會趨勢就係核爆都好第二日都係要返工"},{"pid":"aad0c05aef196fffa1e3afa319ccc0d61f2ebc41","tid":824030,"uid":165298,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:51:41.000Z","msg":"好出奇咩"},{"pid":"6e693fa330a148205d002df76c0db4eb4